These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
Beverage: tea, hot-chocolate
Movie-Genre: musical, mystery
Sport: parkour, lacrosse
Transport: subway, airplane
1. Transport:airplane is on the left or right of Sport:lacrosse##3
2. Beverage:hot-chocolate is in an even position##4
3. Movie-Genre:mystery == Beverage:tea##1
4. Transport:airplane is on the right of Transport:subway##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Beverage      | tea  | hot-chocolate   |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery     | musical   |
| Sport         | lacrosse | parkour |
| Transport     | subway | airplane    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
Food: kale, asparagus
Movie-Genre: animation, zombie
Pet: ferret, goldfish
Transport: helicopter, boat
1. Pet:goldfish is in an odd position##4
2. Movie-Genre:animation == Transport:boat##1
3. Food:asparagus is on the right of Movie-Genre:zombie##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Food          | kale     | asparagus |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | animation  |
| Pet           | goldfish         | ferret     |
| Transport     | helicopter   | boat    |

 #################################
 
