2. Nationality:argentine is on the far left or far right##3
3. Job:scientist == Nationality:american##1
4. Pet:ferret is on the left of Nationality:argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |
| Job           | scientist | photographer    |
| Nationality   | american       | argentine |
| Pet           | ferret         | guinea-pig    |
| Sport         | basketball    | rowing   |

